Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:25.39,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\3c&H8A83E8&}即便迷失道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:30.90,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\3c&H8A83E8&}只因有你相伴
